reviewText: Just what I was looking for
Even though it was from 1992, the drag racing was real and more fun to watch that current top fuel and funny cars.

I was very pleased to find this original DVD at a great price that is becoming much harder to locate. It is where I all started. All the fastest street car stuff started at this race and it was very cool. Perfect condition and shipped fast. Thanks.
Is on DVD but the video quality leaves much to be desired- it looked like it was taken directly from a VHS tape.
+SO  COOOOL !,  GOOOOOD memories. don't tell me how many words to use , I am a man, i get to the point !!!!!!.
